Class ZebraBeaconFilter

java.lang.Object
com.zebra.scannercontrol.beacon.entities.ZebraBeaconFilter
public class ZebraBeaconFilter extends Object
This class is use to send the beacon filter values via the IDcsBeaconEvent interface 'ZebraBeaconFilter' object should be send from the client application via the callback
